re of a thing seen at a distance], (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to see if it moved:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K:) as though he sought, or desired, its motion and change. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstHAl AljahaAma","text_ar":"استحال الجَهَامَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He looked at"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the waterless clouds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the clouds that had poured forth their water, to see if they changed"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moved"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He reckoned it"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHaAl","text_ar":"مُحَال"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"absurd, inconsistent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: see above]. (KL.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}